    public static enum AnswerFormat.Type
extends java.lang.Enum<AnswerFormat.Type>
implements AnswerFormat.QuestionType
    The type of question. (read-only)

    The type provides a default StepBody for that type of question. A custom StepLayout implementation may provide it's own StepBody rather than using the default provided by this AnswerFormat.
